 is a condition that poses an immediate risk to the public and can include downed wires that may be sparking or near water downed poles trees that have fallen on power lines never go near or touch a power line letting im know about safety hazards helps prevent phone lines from becoming overloaded and helps us prioritize work × more from im sign up now pay online for free with paperless billing pay online for free with paperless billing learn more about outage safety tips outage safety tips keep you and your loved ones safe during a power outage how we restore power learn more how we restore power learn the steps im takes to quickly and safely get the power back on find out how save energy save money save energy save money back to top were sorry there was an error enrolling your account in paperless billing for more information contact the customer operations center at  × were sorry there was an error enrolling your account in paperless billing for more information contact the customer operations center at  × you already go online to do business with im try paperless billing and you can pay your bills online for free from your checking account – immediate payment notification now available help the environment by using less paper receive email notification when your bill is ready enjoy convenience – get online access to all of your bills paperless billing i have read and agree to the billing terms  conditions × sign up for alerts subscribing to im alerts gives you instant notification for billing  payments  avoid late payments and disconnection outage updates  find out if theres an outage at your address and when power will be back on loading video × log in login user id password remember user id forgot user id  password register register search search website  indiana michigan power  home my account safety save energy news  info contact us log in register home my account outages  problems safety save energy news  info contact us search mobile menu search website  tw