o your account the next indiana michigan power business day payments made after  pm est on a weekend or on a holiday will take up to  business days to post pay by credit  debit card w fee pay immediately by credit debit some atm cards electronic check business customers electronic check only  fee collected by our partner billmatrix more details billmatrix payments the service fee will be charged by the service provider billmatrix while you will be paying your account with indiana michigan power the full amount of the fee is passed to billmatrix as the provider of this service if you have any questions or problems with your payment please contact billmatrix at 0 you will receive a confirmation code as proof of payment indiana michigan power will be immediately notified of your payment through an electronic memo posting to your electric account payments received prior to  pm est will be posted to your account that evening those made after  pm est on a weekend or on a holiday will post on the next indiana michigan power business day posting schedules may vary on holidays once you have used this service you can check your indiana michigan power account balances and initiate payments  hours a day seven days a week however using this payment option one month does not obligate you to pay this way every month × payments cannot be scheduled in advance youll need your account number login to get it inperson payments options find a payment location check cash or money order payments are limited to those less than 0 more payment options pay by phone pay by mail compare all payment options my bills view bills level payments payment assistance auto monthly withdrawal paperless billing billing  payment alerts more from im find out how save money  energy save money  energy watch now live falconcam sign up now pay online for free with paperless billing pay online for free with paperless billing learn more understanding your residential bill understanding your residential bill select